{"tid":1851372,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"鑒於有大量暴徒用汽油彈襲擊警署，建議處於天橋低位的警署加網巨型罩網","createTime":"2020-01-30T04:15:19.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-30T04:58:02.000Z","uid":230104,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"8574719b25b34a5f0042d598022471c575ba9526","tid":1851372,"uid":230104,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-30T04:15:19.000Z","msg":"好似葵芳警署、觀塘警署、太子警署等既警署，如果暴徒由高處向下投擲，後果嚴重損失慘重，強烈建議帶返個罩<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n強烈譴責暴徒，支持嚴正執法<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"49a3e099b6652c2796771225c306ff3fc10e237d","tid":1851372,"uid":258731,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-30T04:17:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://s.newtalk.tw/album/news/308/5d9705d903228.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.newtalk.tw%2Falbum%2Fnews%2F308%2F5d9705d903228.jpg&h=786cb045&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n港共正利用武漢肺炎進行第9步：<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">種族清洗</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n透過邊境不設防<br />\n高調宣揚非本地人士免費優先治療武漢肺炎<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n蓄意引導大量染病支那人來港<br />\n摧毀香港已經長期超負荷的醫療系統，令香港人大規模感染<br />\n而無法隔離或治理<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><br />\n中共打算將香港將變成武漢，市民無法睇醫生，橫屍街頭<br />\n意圖對香港人進行大屠殺</strong></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/censored.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n香港獨立 港中區隔<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n香港獨立 港中區隔<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><br />\n而家已經係獨立最佳時機，你，仲等緊啲咩<br />\n香港人，仲唔反佢老母？</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n港共正利用武漢肺炎進行第9步：種族清洗 <br />\n香港人，仲唔反佢老母<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1851323\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1851323</a>"},{"pid":"286f25f3ad9f3e1a758a47d7e509c5c79fc09791","tid":1851372,"uid":230104,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-30T04:23:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"06c7cd2752518f6bffbbff452030d167ebc7551b","tid":1851372,"uid":108337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-30T04:24:13.000Z","msg":"空投口罩"},{"pid":"e634927c266293e448571dd67e564624b3fa7a89","tid":1851372,"uid":230104,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"06c7cd2752518f6bffbbff452030d167ebc7551b","tid":1851372,"uid":108337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-30T04:24:13.000Z","msg":"空投口罩"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-30T04:25:24.000Z","msg":"呢個可以"},{"pid":"00e3d8f716bb43d472dfd34bccdb34b28e3f866e","tid":1851372,"uid":228955,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-30T04:58:02.000Z","msg":"冇用啦全部都係黑警自己做邊有人 掉好似玩玩具咁樣 完全冇威脅性"}]}